\par }\pard \qj \fi720\li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\nowidctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlcont\ilvl0\ls0\pnrnot0\pndec }\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 \cbpat8 {\fs24 - Reinmar z Bielawy, tak?
